Hey, what did you get for
your birthday!?

Hey, you wanna play
catch the knife?
Man, I SUCK at this game.

caught your son doing...
But where did I go wrong?!

Hey, Joey! You wanna
eat me?

Hey, Stacey, d'you wanna
go to the prom with me?

Uh, I'm sorry but
I'm a ghost.

-Hey, buddy, you wanna take this outside?!

-Wow, what a lovely evening!
-This was a really good idea.
Don't jump! You have so much to live for!
You have room for a muffin?!
Why won't you let me die?!
Hey, baby, are you an angel?
I am a very tall midget.

Hey, buddy! Turn that frown
upside down!

Subscribe to TomSka for
more videos
And go to...and go to, uhm...

And check out Bravest Warriors on
Cartoon Hangover!
